  "excerpt": "<p>If you\u2019re interested in claiming exemptions for the <strong>2016</strong> tax year <strong>only</strong>, select the links below.</p><div class=\"box-content information-lightweight\"><p><strong>Note:</strong> The links on this page take you to pages about health coverage exemptions that apply for the 2016 tax year. Planning ahead for exemptions? <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"eb1035b3-0f18-43e8-b27f-f146bbb1c5ac\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37591\" data-entity-bundle=\"explainer\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/\" title=\"Health coverage exemptions: Forms &amp; how to apply\">See exemption information for the <strong>2017</strong> tax year</a>. Your 2017 taxes are due in April 2018.</p></div>",
  "content": "<p>If you\u2019re interested in claiming exemptions for the <strong>2016</strong> tax year <strong>only</strong>, select the links below.</p><div class=\"box-content information-lightweight\"><p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;The links on this page take you to pages about health coverage exemptions that apply for the 2016 tax year. Planning ahead for exemptions?&nbsp;<a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"eb1035b3-0f18-43e8-b27f-f146bbb1c5ac\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37591\" data-entity-bundle=\"explainer\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/\" title=\"Health coverage exemptions: Forms &amp; how to apply\">See exemption information for the&nbsp;<strong>2017</strong>&nbsp;tax year</a>. Your 2017 taxes are due in April 2018.</p></div><h3>2016 income-related exemptions</h3><ul><li>The lowest-priced coverage available to you, through either a <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/marketplace-affordability\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">Marketplace</a> or <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/employer-affordability\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">job-based plan</a>, would cost more than 8.05% of your household income</li><li>You don\u2019t have to file a tax return because <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/income-below-threshold\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">your income is below the level that requires you to file</a></li></ul><h3>2016 health coverage-related exemptions</h3><ul><li>You were <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/short-gap\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">uninsured for no more than 2 consecutive months of the year</a></li><li>You lived in a state that <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/secretary-hardship\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">didn\u2019t expand its Medicaid program but you would have qualified if it had</a></li><li>You enrolled a child in the <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/medicaid-chip-denied\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">Children\u2019s Health Insurance Program (CHIP) during the 2016 Open Enrollment period and didn\u2019t have coverage for the child earlier in the year</a></li></ul><h3>2016 group membership exemptions</h3><ul><li>You\u2019re a member of a <a href=\"/glossary/federally-recognized-tribe\" title=\"glossary\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"9c41b716-e79f-4184-8315-c563389c9f2f\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"34851\" data-internal-href=\"/node/34851\">federally recognized tribe</a> or <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/tribal\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">eligible for services through an Indian Health Services provider</a></li><li>You\u2019re a member of a recognized <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/healthcare-sharing-ministry\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">health care sharing ministry</a></li><li>You\u2019re a member of a <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/religion\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">recognized religious sect with religious objections to insurance</a>, including Social Security and Medicare</li></ul><h3>Other 2016 exemptions</h3><ul><li>You\u2019re <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/incarceration\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">incarcerated</a> (serving a term in prison or jail)</li><li>You\u2019re a <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/resident-alien\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">U.S. citizen living abroad, a certain type of non-citizen, or not lawfully present</a> (learn more about the definition of <a href=\"/immigrants/lawfully-present-immigrants\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"f18d9d3a-ca34-4193-bb4f-07610fbf66f7\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36501\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/immigrants/lawfully-present-immigrants/\" title=\"Coverage for lawfully present immigrants\">\u201clawfully present\u201d</a>)</li><li>You experienced one of the hardships below</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>2016 hardship exemptions and forms</h2><p>In addition to the exemptions above, you may qualify for a \u201chardship\u201d exemption. Hardships are life situations that keep you from getting health insurance.</p><p>To claim a hardship exemption, you must fill out a paper application and mail it to the Marketplace. For details and forms, follow the links below.</p><p>Hardships that qualify you for exemptions include:</p><ol><li>You <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/homeless\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">were homeless</a></li><li>You were evicted in the past 6 months or <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/eviction\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">were facing eviction or foreclosure</a></li><li>You <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/utilities-shut-off\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">received a shut-off notice from a utility company</a></li><li>You recently <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/domestic-violence\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">experienced domestic violence</a></li><li>You recently <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/death-in-family\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">experienced the death of a close family member</a></li><li>You <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/disaster\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">experienced a fire, flood, or other natural or human-caused disaster</a> that caused substantial damage to your property</li><li>You <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/bankruptcy\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">filed for bankruptcy</a></li><li>You had <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/owe-medical-expenses\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">medical expenses you couldn\u2019t pay</a> that resulted in substantial debt</li><li>You experienced <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/care-for-family\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">unexpected increases in necessary expenses due to caring for an ill, disabled, or aging family member</a></li><li>You expect to <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/medicaid-chip-denied\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">claim a child as a tax dependent who\u2019s been denied coverage in Medicaid and CHIP</a>, and another person is required by court order to give medical support to the child. In this case, you don't have the pay the penalty for the child.</li><li>As a <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/eligible-based-on-appeal\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">result of an eligibility appeals decision</a>, you\u2019re eligible for enrollment in a qualified health plan (QHP) through the Marketplace, lower costs on your monthly premiums, or cost-sharing reductions for a time period when you weren\u2019t enrolled in a QHP through the Marketplace</li><li>You were <a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/secretary-hardship\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">determined ineligible for Medicaid because your state didn\u2019t expand eligibility for Medicaid</a> under the Affordable Care Act</li><li><a href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee#/results/2016/details/coverage-canceled\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"502e1f0b-ce3d-4282-bb3f-1f8a098849bd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37406\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/health-coverage-exemptions/exemptions-from-the-fee/\" title=\"Exemptions from the requirement to have health insurance\">Your individual insurance plan was canceled</a> and you believe other Marketplace plans are unaffordable</li><li>If you experienced another hardship in obtaining health insurance, download the <a href=\"/exemption-form-instructions\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"bb8e0df7-9a79-44ed-b9bc-39b1ebaf5ebf\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37656\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" data-internal-href=\"/exemption-form-instructions/\" title=\"Download health coverage exemption forms\">hardship exemption application</a></li></ol>",
  "url": "/2016-exemptions",
  "insurance-status": ""
}